    "description": "Revolution Co., Ltd. engages in the real estate resale business in Japan. It operates through four segments: Real Estate Business, Investment Business, Real Estate Credit Business, and Crowdfunding Business. The company is involved in real estate sale, brokerage services, and management of general rental properties; operation of a wholesale financial business, which offers back financing funds to lenders that handle real estate-backed loans; operation of a crowdfunding business; and investment in SPCs, domestic, and foreign companies, as well as financial products, such as securities. It also engages in asset management, rental, and metropolitan property buying and selling businesses. The company was formerly known as Harakosan Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Revolution Co., Ltd. in November 2019. The company was founded in 1986 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan. Revolution Co., Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of FO1 LLC."
